ZH: 宽恕是一种美德。
EN: Forgiveness is a virtue.
ZH: 请你宽恕他的过错。
EN: Please forgive his mistake.
ZH: 她拥有宽恕他人的心。
EN: She has a forgiving heart towards others.
ZH: 我们应该学会宽恕过去的错误。
EN: We should learn to forgive past mistakes.
ZH: 宽恕是建立健康关系的重要一环。
EN: Forgiveness is an important part of building healthy relationships.
ZH: 他请求宽恕并保证不再犯错。
EN: He asked for forgiveness and promised not to make the same mistake again.
ZH: 宽恕别人是对自己的一种解脱。
EN: Forgiving others is a form of liberation for oneself.
ZH: 他的宽恕使得我们得以和解。
EN: His forgiveness allowed us to reconcile.
ZH: 家人之间需要宽恕和理解。
EN: Forgiveness and understanding are needed among family members.
ZH: 不管怎样，我们都应该保持宽恕的心态。
EN: Regardless of the situation, we should maintain a forgiving attitude.
ZH: 宽恕并不容易，但是它能够带来内心的平静。
EN: Forgiveness is not easy, but it can bring inner peace.
ZH: 凡事宽恕别人，也希望别人宽恕自己。
EN: Forgive others in all matters, and hope to be forgiven by others as well.
ZH: 宽恕是一个长久而持续的过程。
EN: Forgiveness is a long and ongoing process.
ZH: 我选择宽恕他的过失，而不是怀恨在心。
EN: I choose to forgive his mistake instead of holding grudges.
ZH: 宽恕可以改变一个人的生活。
EN: Forgiveness can change a person's life.
ZH: 宽恕对个人和社会都有积极的影响。
EN: Forgiveness has positive effects on both individuals and society.
ZH: 宽恕是我树立健康人际关系的基石。
EN: Forgiveness is the cornerstone of building healthy interpersonal relationships.
ZH: 宽恕需要真正的善良和宽宏大量。
EN: Forgiveness requires genuine kindness and magnanimity.
ZH: 宽恕不是放弃，而是释放内心的负担。
EN: Forgiveness is not about giving up, but about releasing the burden in the heart.
ZH: 宽恕他人是修炼自己的一种方式。
EN: Forgiving others is a way to cultivate oneself.
